Achievements.Name: Pound-for-Pound Champion
Achievements.Description: Win the UFC Championship in each weight class in Career Mode.

Achievements.Name: Undisputed Champion
Achievements.Description: Win the UFC Championship with a fighter in Career Mode.

Achievements.Name: Hall of Famer

Achievements.Name: Call me "No Touch!"

Achievements.Name: Where's my bonus check?

Achievements.Name: Student of the game.

Achievements.Name: Purple Belt

Achievements.Name: Black Belt

Achievements.Name: Two of my favorites!

Achievements.Name: Wanted: Flying Mouthpieces
